item.title: CVE-2019-1003022|2024-08-05T03:00:19.439Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20monitoring%20plugin
item.description: A denial of service vulnerability exists in Jenkins Monitoring Plugin 1.74.0 and earlier in PluginImpl.java that allows attackers to kill threads running on the Jenkins master.
